lead_paragraph: Sunderland have decided against handing new deals to strikers  Steven Fletcher and Danny Graham, defender Wes Brown and goalkeeper Steve Harper, the Premier League club said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Sunderland Releases Fletcher, Graham, Brown and Harper
headline.main: Sunderland Releases Fletcher, Graham, Brown and Harper
